---
layout: base.njk
---

<div class="pt-16">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[60vw] h-[40vh] pointer-events-none">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 600 400" class="w-full h-full">
        <path d="M600,400 L600,200 Q400,100 200,200 T0,300 L0,400 Z" fill="#7B2D3B" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-20">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-headline text-charcoal font-semibold mb-8">
        Stop Shrinking.
      </h1>
      
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 whitespace-pre-line">
        You learned how to survive.
        Now you learn how to take up space.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        <a href="#breaking-point" class="btn-primary">
          Enter the Society
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/manifesto/" class="text-charcoal/70 hover:text-charcoal link-underline font-medium transition-colors">
          Read the Manifesto
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Breaking Point Section -->
  <section id="breaking-point" class="relative">
    <div class="curved-divider" style="height: 80px;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="height: 80px;">
        <path d="M0,120 L0,60 Q300,0 600,60 T1200,60 L1200,120 Z" fill="#7B2D3B" fill-opacity="0.1"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-bone py-20 md:py-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-micro text-oxblood mb-6 block">The Breaking Point</span>
        
        <div class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-charcoal leading-[1.8] mb-10 whitespace-pre-line">
          2025 cracked something open. The emotional labor. The over-apologizing. 
          Being competent but exhausted. The constant shrinking to make everyone else comfortable.

          And then—the moment you realized your space matters. That your competence 
          isn't a favor you grant. That your presence isn't an apology.
        </div>
        
        <a href="#what-is" class="btn-primary">
          I'm Done Shrinking.
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What Is a Heifer Section -->
  <section id="what-is" class="relative">
    <div class="curved-divider" style="height: 60px;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="height: 60px;">
        <path d="M0,120 L0,60 Q300,0 600,60 T1200,60 L1200,120 Z" fill="#5A6348" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-bone py-20 md:py-28 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-[8vw] items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="text-micro text-oxblood mb-4 block">What Is a Heifer?</span>
            
            <h2 class="font-serif text-headline-sm text-charcoal mb-8">
              Southern Steel. Self-Sufficient. Composed.
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <p class="font-sans text-base text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
                In the South, "heifer" was never just a word. It meant a female who handles her own. 
                Who doesn't wait for permission. Who moves through the world with competence and quiet confidence.
              </p>
              <p class="font-sans text-base text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
                We're reclaiming it. Not loud. Not small. Not asking. Just handling what needs to be 
                handled—with class, with backbone, with the kind of strength that doesn't need to announce itself.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-cream-dark rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 30" class="w-[200px] h-[30px] mb-8">
              <path d="M10,25 Q100,5 190,25" fill="none" stroke="#C9A961" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.7"/>
            </svg>
            
            <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-charcoal/80 italic leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">
              "A heifer doesn't shrink. She doesn't apologize for her competence. 
              She doesn't explain her boundaries. She simply handles her own."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Work Section -->
  <section id="work" class="relative">
    <div class="curved-divider" style="height: 60px;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="height: 60px;">
        <path d="M0,120 L0,60 Q300,0 600,60 T1200,60 L1200,120 Z" fill="#7B2D3B" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-bone py-20 md:py-28 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-micro text-oxblood mb-4 block">The Work</span>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-headline-sm text-charcoal">Four Pillars</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/60 border border-oxblood/10 rounded-2xl p-8 min-h-[280px] card-lift">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Emotional Clarity</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Understanding what you feel and why. Separating your emotions from other people's expectations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/60 border border-oxblood/10 rounded-2xl p-8 min-h-[280px] card-lift">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Corporate Reality</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Navigating systems that weren't built for you. Playing the game without losing yourself.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/60 border border-oxblood/10 rounded-2xl p-8 min-h-[280px] card-lift">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Boundaries & Backbone</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Saying no without explaining. Holding the line without apology.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/60 border border-oxblood/10 rounded-2xl p-8 min-h-[280px] card-lift">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Ownership</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Taking up space. Claiming your competence. Owning your impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Journal Preview Section -->
  <section id="journal" class="relative">
    <div class="curved-divider" style="height: 60px;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="height: 60px;">
        <path d="M0,120 L0,60 Q300,0 600,60 T1200,60 L1200,120 Z" fill="#5A6348" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-bone py-20 md:py-28 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <span class="text-micro text-oxblood mb-4 block">Journal</span>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-headline-sm text-charcoal">Latest Notes</h2>
          </div>
          <a href="/essays/" class="btn-primary text-sm py-3 px-6">
            View All
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {%- for essay in collections.essays | limit(3) -%}
            {% include "essay-card.njk" %}
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Manifesto Callout Section -->
  <section id="manifesto-callout" class="relative">
    <div class="relative h-[100px] overflow-hidden">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-[100px]">
        <path d="M0,0 L0,60 Q300,120 600,60 T1200,60 L1200,0 Z" fill="#EDE9E2"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-cream-dark py-24 md:py-36 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-headline-md text-charcoal mb-8">
          You Do Not Need Permission.
        </h2>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-10">
          The manifesto is for the woman who is done shrinking. Who is ready to take up space 
          without apology. Who knows that her competence is not a favor she grants to the world.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/manifesto/" class="btn-primary">
          Read the Manifesto
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
